","tid":1269154,"uid":216105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:35:33.000Z","msg":"times<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca85ac3198aaca77c35cd7d383f894bed2e2646","tid":1269154,"uid":3937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3775b26191e1ccac08c88c5a01b37994e466f095","tid":1269154,"uid":85295,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:20:42.000Z","msg":"想問下北海道租車買埋etc pass係咪去toyota好d?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:11:30.000Z","msg":"其他公司都有HEP<br />\n租邊間就自己諗<br />\n我自己就大個幾間（orix nissan nippon toyota times）邊間平租邊間"},{"pid":"1ae5e9719743b475c08b3e48d3bc1772d9ffb7e9","tid":1269154,"uid":187726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:12:31.000Z","msg":"其實上tabirai都有齊晒咁多間公司嘅plan，日文版網站會平過中文版，不過多數冇得指定車款<br />\n自己就租過Toyota、Times、Nippon、Honda（得北海道有）<br />\n總體嚟講Toyota &gt; Honda（分店少要扣分）&gt;&gt; Times = Nippon<br />\n價錢(貴到平)就Toyota = Honda &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Times<br />\n如果唔同地方還車要睇埋每間公司個乘捨料金，Times個料金係最平咁滯，Nippon貴過Times少少，Toyota同Nissan就係最貴<br />\n<br />\nTimes啲車通常洗得唔太乾淨，車身同大銀幕會有啲污漬，同埋車身通常殘啲，多花痕（拎車試過四條鈴都係花晒，唔係買全保嘅人要小心啲check），車內狀況就一架架，有啲熱門平車款都幾殘，試過車頭乘客腳位個櫃桶要勁大力先閂得實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過Times試過免費upgrade車款比我，book 1.5 Hybrid俾SUV Hybrid我<br />\n<br />\nKeep車呢樣嘢Toyota做得好好多，交車時架車內外都係好乾淨，少花痕<br />\n<br />\nOption就間間都係咁上下齋，鐵鈴、傳統非LED黃頭燈、七人單電門呢啲預咗，始終人哋買架齋版同貴版都係咁做生意，但係泊車鏡頭呢啲都會有，最近去Times租架Serena都有360鏡頭、行車線偏離sensor"},{"pid":"d984f094bb32c2e073ba2352ab2cb0a9fbe250de","tid":1269154,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ae5e9719743b475c08b3e48d3bc1772d9ffb7e9","tid":1269154,"uid":187726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB